1669
01:10:14,290 --> 01:10:16,720
♪ (Kto v tom nevyrastal, nemôže to pochopiť.) ♪

1670
01:10:16,720 --> 01:10:19,570
♪ (Zaujímalo by ma, prečo to títo chalani robia roky.) ♪

1671
01:10:19,570 --> 01:10:22,540
♪ (Tak nech každý, kto sa odváži, kričí a pridá sa k nám:) ♪

1672
01:10:22,540 --> 01:10:25,060
♪ (Hore so slovom, so slovom, so slovom vždycky hore!) ♪

1673
01:10:25,060 --> 01:10:26,340
Trepeš pičoviny, Mišo,

1674
01:10:26,340 --> 01:10:27,550
najodpornejšie vlasy má

1675
01:10:27,550 --> 01:10:28,320
Kolman, už aj

1676
01:10:28,320 --> 01:10:29,940
šediny mu začínajú rašiť.

1677
01:10:32,480 --> 01:10:33,390
Ale nik nemá tak

1678
01:10:33,390 --> 01:10:35,240
mastnú gebuľu jak tuto Kim.

1679
01:10:35,470 --> 01:10:36,540
To je viac oleja jak

1680
01:10:36,540 --> 01:10:37,730
z nedeľnej kačice.

1681
01:10:38,660 --> 01:10:40,040
Peder, tento tvoj detinský

1682
01:10:40,040 --> 01:10:41,550
humor ma už nedokáže rozhodiť.

1683
01:10:44,930 --> 01:10:46,400
Aj tak si otrasná.

1684
01:10:52,670 --> 01:10:53,780
Sleduj, ako sa

1685
01:10:53,780 --> 01:10:55,250
získava otrokyňa.

1686
01:10:58,270 --> 01:10:59,080
Čo to je?

1687
01:11:03,740 --> 01:11:04,440
Čo?

1688
01:11:04,440 --> 01:11:05,170
Ty...

1689
01:11:05,170 --> 01:11:06,250
za päť korún

1690
01:11:06,270 --> 01:11:07,510
budeš orať

1691
01:11:08,370 --> 01:11:09,640
na mojom poli.

1692
01:11:10,410 --> 01:11:11,530
Za päť korún?

1693
01:11:12,010 --> 01:11:12,750
Dobre.

1694
01:11:17,520 --> 01:11:18,150
