Vždy rád spomínam, ako som ho

2433
01:46:48,590 --> 01:46:49,950
zdrogovaného odpanil.

2434
01:46:51,320 --> 01:46:52,610
Každopádne sa teraz musím

2435
01:46:52,610 --> 01:46:53,970
sústrediť na iné veci.

2436
01:46:54,410 --> 01:46:56,050
Vasil sa niekde stratil,

2437
01:46:56,050 --> 01:46:58,260
Meky sa úplne prestal ozývať.

2438
01:46:59,540 --> 01:47:01,400
Hlavne, že si naplánoval nový koncert

2439
01:47:01,400 --> 01:47:03,610
na Čiernom Balogu a krst albumu.

2440
01:47:04,370 --> 01:47:06,040
Na budúci týždeň.

2441
01:47:05,830 --> 01:47:06,830
[Nightwork - Já jsem gay!]

2442
01:47:06,750 --> 01:47:08,140
Nedáva to zmysel, Dano.

2443
01:47:08,840 --> 01:47:10,320
Celý turnaj sa rozpadá.

2444
01:47:12,740 --> 01:47:14,740
Pane, Jerguš Gombit.

2445
01:47:15,070 --> 01:47:16,900
čo ho odsúdili za ten ohavný čin.

2446
01:47:16,900 --> 01:47:18,040
Čo je s ním teraz?

2447
01:47:18,160 --> 01:47:19,560
Odkiaľ to mám vedieť?

2448
01:47:20,890 --> 01:47:22,320
Ja som bol na tom súde

2449
01:47:22,850 --> 01:47:24,920
len kvôli jednému mladému krásnemu

2450
01:47:24,920 --> 01:47:27,300
stážistovi, na ktorého som mal zálusk.

2451
01:47:28,430 --> 01:47:29,590
Prečo sa pýtaš?

2452
01:47:32,320 --> 01:47:33,930
Občas mávam také sny,

2453
01:47:34,760 --> 01:47:36,340
skôr sú to nočné mory

2454
01:47:36,410 --> 01:47:38,020
po ktorých sa prebúdzam spotený

2455
01:47:38,020 --> 01:47:39,290
a väčšinou aj zesraný.

2456
01:47:39,770 --> 01:47:41,420
Začína to v nejakom zatuchnutom

2457
01:47:41,420 --> 01:47:42,980
čiernom zrube, niečo ako

2458
01:47:42,980 --> 01:47:45,380
štvorhviezdičkový hotel v Rimavskej Sobote.

2459
01:47:43,620 --> 01:47:46,940
Dôležité je to, čo máte v srdci, nie ako vyzeráte.

2460
01:47:45,460 --> 01:47:49,430
Pán Žbirka, pán Žbirka, však vám vypálilo bradavicu, tak ako to, že nie ste rád?

2461
01:47:45,940 --> 01:47:49,190
Vchádzam do izby, z ktorej počuť rôzne anglické slovíčka,

2462
01:47:49,830 --> 01:47:51,050
I want to hold your hand.

2463
01:47:49,190 --> 01:47:51,070
takže je jasné, že je tam Meky Žbirka.

2464
01:47:51,130 --> 01:47:52,070
Yesterday.

2465
01:47:51,450 --> 01:47:53,050
No a je tam s ním nejaký pán Patkaň

2466
01:47:53,050 --> 01:47:54,710
a hlavne aj Jerguš Gombit.

2467
01:47:54,970 --> 01:47:56,490
Ale Žbirkovi nevidím do tváre,

2468
01:47:56,490 --> 01:47:58,350
iba ho počujem ako dookola rozpráva

2469
01:47:58,350 --> 01:48:00,610
o Beatles a Paulovi McCartneym.

2470
01:48:01,730 --> 01:48:03,840
Často sa rozprávajú práve o turnaji,

2471
01:48:03,840 --> 01:48:06,220
ale vždy sa zobudím a musím vyprať obliečky.

2472
01:48:06,800 --> 01:48:09,130
Neviete, čo tieto sny môžu znamenať?

2473
01:48:11,510 --> 01:48:13,090
Mne sa zas často sníva

2474
01:48:13,090 --> 01:48:14,090
o tebe, Dano.

2475
01:48:14,740 --> 01:48:17,230
Neviem, čo tie tvoje preludy znamenajú.

2476
01:48:20,780 --> 01:48:22,780
Ale plastický chirurg, čo mi robil

2477
01:48:22,780 --> 01:48:24,440
ritné implantáty sa volal

2478
01:48:24,440 --> 01:48:25,790
MUDr. Igor Patkaň.

2479
01:48:25,990 --> 01:48:27,540
Neviem, či ti to pomôže.

2480
01:48:34,360 --> 01:48:37,230
(Miro Žbirka ..., Lajos.)

2481
01:48:44,620 --> 01:48:46,210
Počkaj Drevo, poď sem.

2482
01:48:45,650 --> 01:48:51,880
(To je ten blbec, čo sa stále poserie, len sa všade motá, stále je stratený, zablúdený)

2483
01:48:54,660 --> 01:48:55,990
Vedel si, že každý štvrtý

2484
01:48:55,990 --> 01:48:57,430
človek na svete je moslim?

2485
01:48:58,650 --> 01:48:59,620
A bude nás viac.

2486
01:49:01,510 --> 01:49:02,130
Super.

2487
01:49:03,970 --> 01:49:04,610
Poď za mnou.

2488
01:49:05,970 --> 01:49:10,060


2489
01:49:11,800 --> 01:49:13,800
Mám tu niečo, čo by si mohol odkúpiť.

2490
01:48:52,710 --> 01:48:53,710
[Areeb - Al habib al awwal]

2491
01:49:17,360 --> 01:49:17,880
Toto.

2492
01:49:23,200 --> 01:49:24,090
Vieš, čo to je?

2493
01:49:25,840 --> 01:49:27,720
Nejaká arabská pičovina?

2494
01:49:28,140 --> 01:49:30,140
Slzy afgánskych

2495
01:49:30,830 --> 01:49:31,580
polosirôt.

2496
01:49:31,580 --> 01:49:32,690
A stačí ich pár vypiť,

2497
01:49:32,690 --> 01:49:33,970
alebo sa v nich vykúpať

2498
01:49:34,180 --> 01:49:35,490
a tvoje telo sa dostane...

2499
01:49:37,220 --> 01:49:38,930
do svojej pôvodnej podoby.

2500
01:49:40,310 --> 01:49:42,270
Pri vážnych zraneniach sa používajú

2501
01:49:42,270 --> 01:49:43,680
ako súčasť takzvaného

2502
01:49:43,680 --> 01:49:45,880
Arabského rituálu znovuzrodenia.

2503
01:49:46,410 --> 01:49:48,290
Predám ti fľaštičku za štyri eurá.

2504
01:49:49,010 --> 01:49:50,050
Ja nemám záujem!

2505
01:49:49,830 --> 01:49:51,060
Som totálne

2506
01:49:51,060 --> 01:49:52,110
na mizine.

2507
01:49:52,390 --> 01:49:52,980
Počuješ?!

2508
01:49:53,040 --> 01:49:54,730
Predal som síce 70 litrov

2509
01:49:54,730 --> 01:49:56,510
tejto kokotiny Mekymu Žbirkovi,

2510
01:49:57,720 --> 01:49:58,760
ale Šaňo Fekete

2511
01:49:58,760 --> 01:50:00,130
to zo mňa všetko vycical.

2512
01:50:00,530 --> 01:50:01,790
Pamätaj moje slová, Drevo.

2513
01:50:01,940 --> 01:50:03,350
Veľký Alah to všetko vidí.

2514
01:50:03,350 --> 01:50:04,830
Všetko vidí a potrestá ťa,

2515
01:50:04,830 --> 01:50:05,860
ty kurva lakomá!

2516
01:50:07,660 --> 01:50:09,060
Dámy a páni, začína

2517
01:50:09,060 --> 01:50:10,590
nám posledná disciplína

2518
01:50:10,590 --> 01:50:12,260
turnaja Mekyho Žbirku!

2519
01:50:12,260 --> 01:50:13,400
Dnes tak ako obvykle

2520
01:50:13,400 --> 01:50:14,760
máme mierne technické pro-

2521
01:50:15,810 --> 01:50:16,840
S jeho špinavým

2522
01:50:16,840 --> 01:50:18,740
cigánskym fotrom prichádza

2523
01:50:18,740 --> 01:50:21,370
hnedý Romák, Šaňo Fekete!

2524
01:50:22,110 --> 01:50:23,830
Nasleduje navoňaná šľapka

2525
01:50:23,830 --> 01:50:25,380
s jej prerastenou pasáčkou,

2526
01:50:25,380 --> 01:50:27,060
Zuzana de Merde!

2527
01:50:27,560 --> 01:50:28,560
[Los Del Rio - Macarena]

2528
01:50:28,730 --> 01:50:30,620
V prievode bývalého kriminálnika

2529
01:50:30,620 --> 01:50:32,190
prichádza obdarený Maďar,

2530
01:50:32,190 --> 01:50:34,960
Gábor Székesfehérvár Balaton Szabadi Sóstó.

2531
01:50:35,610 --> 01:50:37,050
A ako inak, posledný,

2532
01:50:37,050 --> 01:50:39,350
spoločne s jeho spráchniveným frajerom

2533
01:50:39,350 --> 01:50:40,520
Dano Jebo!

2534
01:50:40,900 --> 01:50:41,960
No tak pardon.

2535
01:50:42,010 --> 01:50:43,120
Jano Jebo!

2536
01:50:43,120 --> 01:50:44,440
Jano Jebo, vážení.

2537
01:50:45,410 --> 01:50:47,000
Poprosím mohutný aplaus

2538
01:50:47,000 --> 01:50:48,740
pre všetkých súťažiacich!

2539
01:50:51,120 --> 01:50:52,690
Tak buďte už ticho.

2540
01:50:53,430 --> 01:50:55,660
Ticho!

2541
01:50:58,190 --> 01:50:59,560
Vítam vás vo finále

2542
01:50:59,560 --> 01:51:01,260
turnaja Mekyho Žbirku!

2543
01:51:01,940 --> 01:51:03,580
Kedže naša škola odjakživa

2544
01:51:03,580 --> 01:51:05,010
podporovala rasizmus,

2545
01:51:05,420 --> 01:51:07,380
do labyrintu pôjdu prví Slováci.

2546
01:51:07,970 --> 01:51:09,190
A teda Šaňo Fekete

2547
01:51:11,580 --> 01:51:13,360
spoločne s Danom Drevom.

2548
01:51:14,570 --> 01:51:16,440
Kedže som sa včera skoro udusil

2549
01:51:16,440 --> 01:51:17,770
jeho khokotom,

2550
01:51:17,770 --> 01:51:19,770
ako ďalší vstúpi do labyrintu

2551
01:51:20,100 --> 01:51:21,290
Chvostnatý Gábor!

2552
01:51:21,070 --> 01:51:22,070


2553
01:51:21,790 --> 01:51:26,430


2554
01:51:26,430 --> 01:51:28,240
A ako posledná vstúpi do turnaja

2555
01:51:28,240 --> 01:51:30,230
absolútne nezaujímavá sivá myš

2556
01:51:30,230 --> 01:51:31,420
Zuzana de Merde.

2557
01:51:35,780 --> 01:51:37,780
Víťazom sa stane súťažiaci,

2558
01:51:38,260 --> 01:51:40,770
ktorý ako prvý v bludisku nájde

2559
01:51:41,300 --> 01:51:42,930
Poltársky ozdobný válov

2560
01:51:42,930 --> 01:51:44,760
a dotkne sa ho svojím prštekom.

2561
01:51:45,890 --> 01:51:47,530
Súťažiaci, poďte ku mne.

2562
01:51:48,650 --> 01:51:49,090
Poďte!

2563
01:51:53,060 --> 01:51:54,510
Strácajú sa ľudia

2564
01:51:54,510 --> 01:51:56,800
a dejú sa nevysvetliteľné veci.

2565
01:51:57,360 --> 01:51:59,420
Meky Žbirka úplne prestal komunikovať,

2566
01:51:59,420 --> 01:52:01,050
čo je zvláštne, pretože zajtra

2567
01:52:01,230 --> 01:52:02,780
má mať krst albumu a koncert

2568
01:52:02,780 --> 01:52:04,110
na Čiernom Balogu.

2569
01:52:04,200 --> 01:52:06,010
Turnaj môže byť nebezpečný

2570
01:52:06,370 --> 01:52:08,370
a ja mám morálne právo ho ukončiť.

2571
01:52:08,440 --> 01:52:09,770
Ale mám piči, práve začína

2572
01:52:09,770 --> 01:52:11,060
priamy prenos Muža roku.

2573
01:52:11,270 --> 01:52:12,420
Tak veľa štastia

2574
01:52:12,760 --> 01:52:13,330
prajem.

2575
01:52:13,770 --> 01:52:15,200
Posledná rozlúčka!

2576
01:52:24,290 --> 01:52:25,200
Drž sa.

2577
01:52:27,970 --> 01:52:29,930
Pán školník síce dva dni bez spánku

2578
01:52:29,930 --> 01:52:32,210
fetoval, ale už je čerstvý a pripravený

2579
01:52:32,550 --> 01:52:33,210
zahájiť-

2580
01:52:34,510 --> 01:52:35,120
Čo?

2581
01:52:36,400 --> 01:52:38,160
Alkohol je pliaga.

2582
01:52:39,930 --> 01:52:40,930
[Miro Žbirka - Mám rád]

2583
01:53:02,610 --> 01:53:03,770
Meky Žbirka.

2584
01:53:07,450 --> 01:53:08,790
Meky Žbirka.

2585
01:53:10,900 --> 01:53:11,950
"Zbirka"

2586
01:53:17,840 --> 01:53:18,820
Keď som mal možnosť sa

2587
01:53:18,820 --> 01:53:20,320
s Paul McCartney, Paul McCartney

2588
01:53:20,320 --> 01:53:21,920
Paul McCartney rozprávať.

2589
01:53:33,100 --> 01:53:34,560
It's been a hard day.

2590
01:53:45,160 --> 01:53:46,160
[Parno Graszt - Rávágok a zongorára]

2591
01:53:45,160 --> 01:53:48,000
♪ (Idem si zahrať na klavíri.) ♪

2592
01:53:50,420 --> 01:53:53,220
♪ (Orgán šepká,) ♪

2593
01:53:53,220 --> 01:53:55,790
♪ (Gézuova matka utiekla.) ♪

2594
01:53:55,790 --> 01:53:59,230
♪ (Hej Rómovia, deti.) ♪

2595
01:53:58,470 --> 01:53:59,770
Something's going on.

2596
01:54:00,500 --> 01:54:02,820
Zažni aspoň kúsok sviece.

2597
01:54:06,630 --> 01:54:07,720
Fair play.

2598
01:54:07,830 --> 01:54:10,490
♪ (Orgán šepká,) ♪

2599
01:54:08,010 --> 01:54:08,810
Čo do piče?!

2600
01:54:10,230 --> 01:54:11,070
Kurva.

2601
01:54:10,490 --> 01:54:13,330
♪ (Gézuova matka utiekla.) ♪

2602
01:54:12,810 --> 01:54:13,860
To čo toto je.

2603
01:54:13,360 --> 01:54:16,870
♪ (Hej Rómovia, deti.) ♪

2604
01:54:18,170 --> 01:54:22,680
(Krásna, krásna, ktorej oči sú modré,)

2605
01:54:22,680 --> 01:54:25,940
(ktorej oči sú čierne.)

2606
01:54:29,690 --> 01:54:30,720
Yesterday.

2607
01:54:40,540 --> 01:54:41,710
Biely kvet.

2608
01:54:41,950 --> 01:54:44,210
Pesničky Lennona a McCartneyho.

2609
01:54:44,210 --> 01:54:46,020
McCartneyho, McCartneyho-

2610
01:54:46,950 --> 01:54:48,540
My darling,

2611
01:54:48,540 --> 01:54:50,320
please don't take your love away.

2612
01:54:50,320 --> 01:54:51,260
Love away.

2613
01:54:53,070 --> 01:54:53,910
...love away.

2614
01:55:06,260 --> 01:55:07,780
Minule som bol v Chicagu.

2615
01:55:41,450 --> 01:55:43,190
Čo to požral, ten chlapča?

2616
01:55:43,190 --> 01:55:45,860
Mi to rozleptalo sliznicu, normálne.

2617
01:55:45,860 --> 01:55:47,400
Fuj, to je-

2618
01:55:59,240 --> 01:56:00,150
Zuza!

2619
01:56:07,840 --> 01:56:09,520
Do nemocnici!

2620
01:56:40,060 --> 01:56:41,140
Follow me.

2621
01:56:48,030 --> 01:56:49,280
(Zhni!)

2622
01:56:51,390 --> 01:56:52,230
(Skap!)

2623
01:56:52,910 --> 01:56:53,870
Sufurki!

2624
01:56:53,940 --> 01:56:54,720
Nem!

2625
01:56:58,820 --> 01:57:00,470
Maďar posraný, dig more.

2626
01:57:02,770 --> 01:57:04,270
Nechaj ho, on má len forinty!

2627
01:57:04,270 --> 01:57:05,790
Tie sú ti úplne na piču.

2628
01:57:05,870 --> 01:57:07,200
Nechaj ma na pokoji bráško.

2629
01:57:11,010 --> 01:57:11,620
Ty špina!

2630
01:57:12,030 --> 01:57:13,030
Ty Cigáň!

2631
01:57:13,590 --> 01:57:14,540
Ty zasran!

2632
01:57:14,970 --> 01:57:16,340
Ty kokot posraný.

2633
01:57:15,330 --> 01:57:15,890
Boha.

2634
01:57:16,450 --> 01:57:17,080
Hnedý.

2635
01:57:23,750 --> 01:57:24,850
Bohatstvo!

2636
01:57:23,930 --> 01:57:24,610
Hajzel!

2637
01:57:26,330 --> 01:57:27,080
Do riti.

2638
01:57:32,010 --> 01:57:33,340
Boha, rite.

2639
01:57:36,890 --> 01:57:38,890
Dano, prosím ťa, Dano, čo si slepý?

2640
01:57:39,460 --> 01:57:40,850
Čo nevidíš, že ma tu jebú korene?

2641
01:57:40,850 --> 01:57:42,280
Potrebuješ väčšie dioptrie, Dano?

2642
01:57:42,280 --> 01:57:43,700
Potrebuješ väčšie dioptrie?

2643
01:57:43,400 --> 01:57:45,040
Skurvené dioptrie.

2644
01:57:43,700 --> 01:57:46,610
Potrebuješ väčšie dioptrie, Dano?

2645
01:57:44,350 --> 01:57:46,720
Dano, prosím ťa, však ma tu udusia tie rastliny.

2646
01:57:45,980 --> 01:57:48,090
Skurvené dioptrie.

2647
01:57:46,490 --> 01:57:48,130
Ti už fakt nestačia tie popolníky,

2648
01:57:48,130 --> 01:57:49,320
ty slepec prijebaný?

2649
01:57:50,120 --> 01:57:51,410
Dano prosím ťa, pomôž mi.

2650
01:57:51,410 --> 01:57:53,130
Hneď zajtra ti vrátim tých 16 eur

2651
01:57:53,130 --> 01:57:55,020
čo ti dlžím, zajtra ich máš na stole!

2652
01:57:55,020 --> 01:57:56,050
Ach prosím ťa Dano,

2653
01:57:56,050 --> 01:57:57,750
ešte aj s úrokami ti ich vrátim.

2654
01:58:16,100 --> 01:58:17,080
Díky bráško.

2655
01:58:17,210 --> 01:58:18,240
Díky moc.

2656
01:58:18,460 --> 01:58:19,280
Není zač.

2657
01:58:20,410 --> 01:58:21,140
Počuj,

2658
01:58:21,740 --> 01:58:22,750
tých 16 eur

2659
01:58:23,360 --> 01:58:24,520
teraz nemám Dano.

2660
01:58:25,050 --> 01:58:26,060
To som si myslel.

2661
01:58:28,550 --> 01:58:29,730
Ale vrátim ti ich.

2662
01:58:30,380 --> 01:58:30,990
Fakt.

2663
01:58:30,990 --> 01:58:31,820
Dobre.

2664
01:58:37,170 --> 01:58:38,390
Bežme, poď!

2665
01:58:48,970 --> 01:58:50,270
Je to určite ten válov?

2666
01:58:50,270 --> 01:58:50,830
Neviem!

2667
01:58:50,830 --> 01:58:51,990
Možno je to nejaký iný.

2668
01:58:52,290 --> 01:58:53,660
Jeb na to a ber ho!

2669
01:58:54,250 --> 01:58:55,020
Ber ho!

2670
01:58:55,500 --> 01:58:56,500
[Miro Žbirka - Mám rád]

2671
01:59:11,520 --> 01:59:13,130
Smrdia tu varené potkany.

2672
01:59:13,130 --> 01:59:14,200
To musíme byť na nejakom

2673
01:59:14,200 --> 01:59:15,870
rómskom pohrebisku.

2674
01:59:17,790 --> 01:59:18,800
Však to tu vyzerá jak

2675
01:59:18,800 --> 01:59:19,960
u nás večer v osade.

2676
01:59:23,670 --> 01:59:25,490
To je rimavskosobotský cintorín.

2677
01:59:26,480 --> 01:59:28,390
Boli sme tu s triedou na exkurzii.

2678
01:59:31,070 --> 01:59:31,830
To je oceľ.

2679
01:59:34,080 --> 01:59:35,950
V zbere za to dostaneme 120 korún.

2680
01:59:35,650 --> 01:59:36,870
Jeb teraz na zber!

2681
01:59:37,330 --> 01:59:38,200
Cigoš.

2682
01:59:38,780 --> 01:59:40,200
Sú aj dôležitejšie veci ako

2683
01:59:40,200 --> 01:59:41,390
zber kovošrotu.

2684
01:59:44,410 --> 01:59:45,150
To odvoláš.

2685
01:59:47,580 --> 01:59:48,580
[Miro Žbirka - Bezchybná]

2686
01:59:51,530 --> 01:59:52,770
Dano, čo sa deje?

2687
01:59:53,160 --> 01:59:54,430
Však ja sa s tebou rozdelím.

2688
01:59:54,100 --> 01:59:56,120
Neznášam Žbirkove pesničky.

2689
01:59:56,130 --> 01:59:57,110
Paul McCartney.

2690
02:00:00,410 --> 02:00:01,500
Kto ste, čo chcete?

2691
02:00:01,860 --> 02:00:03,020
Ste tu kvôli tej oceli?

2692
02:00:03,400 --> 02:00:08,070
Môžme to zriešiť fifty-fifty, však sa-

2693
02:00:04,500 --> 02:00:05,300
Jožo Vajda!

2694
02:00:05,500 --> 02:00:07,040
Nie!

2695
02:00:10,650 --> 02:00:12,670
Igor, odhoď ho tam na chvíľu, tam

2696
02:00:12,670 --> 02:00:14,670
hore, presne tam, nech drží

2697
02:00:14,670 --> 02:00:15,740
na tej kosti.

2698
02:00:15,770 --> 02:00:18,360
A hoď ma do tých sĺz afgánskych polosirôt,

2699
02:00:18,360 --> 02:00:19,700
Igor, nech môže začať

2700
02:00:19,700 --> 02:00:20,980
arabský rituál.

2701
02:00:21,430 --> 02:00:22,670
Už sa neviem dočkať

2702
02:00:22,670 --> 02:00:23,980
prvého koncertíku.

2703
02:00:23,980 --> 02:00:25,800
To rozbalím jak za starých čias.

2704
02:00:28,260 --> 02:00:30,160
Pôjdeme teda na rituál.

2705
02:00:31,070 --> 02:00:32,130
Bravčová

2706
02:00:33,300 --> 02:00:34,050
kosť.

2707
02:00:34,930 --> 02:00:35,920
Ohlodaná

2708
02:00:36,750 --> 02:00:38,750
Ivanou Christovou.

2709
02:00:44,430 --> 02:00:45,230
Ruka

2710
02:00:46,560 --> 02:00:47,990
plastického chirurga.

2711
02:00:48,720 --> 02:00:49,500
Sťatá

2712
02:00:50,010 --> 02:00:50,830
nožom

2713
02:00:51,470 --> 02:00:53,010
špinavým jak tvoja mater.

2714
02:00:56,860 --> 02:00:58,360
A už iba krv

2715
02:00:59,100 --> 02:01:00,390
krásavca,

2716
02:01:02,560 --> 02:01:03,830
ktorého tvár

2717
02:01:06,830 --> 02:01:08,430
bude privlastnená.

2718
02:01:15,350 --> 02:01:16,410
Vykvapaná do

2719
02:01:16,410 --> 02:01:18,350
gulášového kotla.

2720
02:01:18,800 --> 02:01:20,710
A Arabský rituál znovuzrodenia

2721
02:01:20,710 --> 02:01:21,940
sa môže začať.

2722
02:01:21,690 --> 02:01:22,690
[Choir of Beirut - Ihmadou Al Rab]

2723
02:01:21,690 --> 02:01:30,230
♪ (Ďakujte Hospodinovi, lebo je dobrý,) ♪

2724
02:01:26,610 --> 02:01:28,420
Strašne rýchlo to išlo všetko.

2725
02:01:28,260 --> 02:01:30,840
...som mal tak, akosi vyletel.

2726
02:01:30,230 --> 02:01:37,420
♪ (lebo naveky trvá Jeho milosť.) ♪

2727
02:01:30,840 --> 02:01:33,740
To je jedna z mála vecí, čo si pamätám.

2728
02:01:33,740 --> 02:01:36,810
A ja som to potom zažil naozaj na vlastnej koži.

2729
02:01:36,820 --> 02:01:38,450
Ja som ležal na hoteli.

2730
02:01:37,420 --> 02:01:41,220
♪ (Chváľte Pána.) ♪

2731
02:01:38,460 --> 02:01:39,660
Nikam nechcem chodiť.

2732
02:01:39,730 --> 02:01:42,590
Bol som maličký, tak o to to bolo také zvláštnejšie.

2733
02:01:41,220 --> 02:01:55,000
♪ (Nech povedia tí, čo sa boja Hospodina:) ♪

2734
02:01:42,640 --> 02:01:44,710
Ty máš výbornú tvár pre rádio.

2735
02:01:44,720 --> 02:01:45,890
Tá známa tvár.

2736
02:01:45,890 --> 02:01:47,680
A aby som to teda dopovedal.

2737
02:01:47,700 --> 02:01:49,550
To bola zašifrovaná správa.

2738
02:01:55,000 --> 02:02:03,000
♪ (Naveky trvá Jeho milosť.) ♪

2739
02:02:03,000 --> 02:02:07,000
♪ (Chváľte Pána.) ♪

2740
02:02:07,270 --> 02:02:08,270
[Miro Žbirka - Biely kvet]

2741
02:02:24,320 --> 02:02:26,720
Čím budem podpisovať autogramy?

2742
02:02:32,280 --> 02:02:33,440
Díky, Igor.

2743
02:02:37,630 --> 02:02:39,030
A ako vyzerám?

2744
02:02:39,300 --> 02:02:40,720
Úchvatne.

2745
02:02:41,210 --> 02:02:42,530
Zmizla vám

2746
02:02:42,640 --> 02:02:43,610
bradavica.

2747
02:02:43,800 --> 02:02:45,380
Nastav ruku Igor.

2748
02:02:51,140 --> 02:02:52,710
Nový album sa blíži.

2749
02:02:52,710 --> 02:02:55,350
Je na čase vybrať krstného otca.

2750
02:03:26,120 --> 02:03:27,190
Dobrý večer,

2751
02:03:29,160 --> 02:03:31,260
skrachované celebrity.

2752
02:03:31,590 --> 02:03:32,770
Teší ma váš záujem

2753
02:03:32,770 --> 02:03:34,580
pokrstiť môj nový album.

2754
02:03:36,080 --> 02:03:38,080
Kto z vás si však na mňa spomenul

2755
02:03:38,080 --> 02:03:40,370
po tom, čo som sa zjebal v Patinciach

2756
02:03:40,370 --> 02:03:41,380
do kyseliny?

2757
02:03:42,720 --> 02:03:43,900
Kto z vás

2758
02:03:44,730 --> 02:03:46,170
ma prišiel navštíviť,

2759
02:03:46,170 --> 02:03:48,630
keď ma previezli do Rimavskej Soboty?

2760
02:03:48,740 --> 02:03:50,860
Trpel som a vy ste ma ignorovali!

2761
02:03:51,170 --> 02:03:52,180
Všetci!

2762
02:03:53,470 --> 02:03:54,330
Všetci.

2763
02:03:54,750 --> 02:03:56,160
Every one of you.

2764
02:03:56,860 --> 02:03:58,860
Keď však ide o krst albumu,

2765
02:03:59,280 --> 02:04:01,170
tak sa začínate vtierať.

2766
02:04:01,170 --> 02:04:01,960
Že, Braňo?

2767
02:04:04,760 --> 02:04:06,020
Miro, počúvaj ma.

2768
02:04:06,020 --> 02:04:07,500
Poslal som ti pohľadnicu,

2769
02:04:07,500 --> 02:04:09,850
kde som ti poprial rýchle zotavenie.

2770
02:04:09,560 --> 02:04:11,220
Nič mi neprišlo, Braňo.

2771
02:04:11,470 --> 02:04:12,760
Žiadna pohľadnica.

2772
02:04:12,800 --> 02:04:13,900
Museli to dojebať

2773
02:04:13,900 --> 02:04:16,140
Cigánky na pošte v Rimavskej Sobote.

2774
02:04:16,140 --> 02:04:18,140
Nenapadá ma iná možnosť.

2775
02:04:19,590 --> 02:04:20,760
Chcel som ti dokonca

2776
02:04:20,760 --> 02:04:22,480
kúpiť darčekový kôš

2777
02:04:22,480 --> 02:04:23,920
a malú bonbonierku,

2778
02:04:27,290 --> 02:04:29,290
ale všetko som prepil.

2779
02:04:29,850 --> 02:04:31,610
Čo tá operácia, Meky?

2780
02:04:31,800 --> 02:04:33,650
Nebuď netrpezlivý, Igor.

2781
02:04:33,810 --> 02:04:35,450
Vieš jak sa hovorí, že

2782
02:04:35,450 --> 02:04:37,120
pomaly ďalej you go.

2783
02:04:39,270 --> 02:04:41,270
Som tak rád, že sa našiel aj

2784
02:04:41,270 --> 02:04:43,340
v radoch plastických chirurgov

2785
02:04:43,340 --> 02:04:44,470
môj fanúšik.

2786
02:04:45,320 --> 02:04:46,600
Páči sa Igorko,

2787
02:04:46,600 --> 02:04:48,450
budeš tú ruku potrebovať.

2788
02:04:49,280 --> 02:04:50,350
Mirko.

2789
02:04:50,490 --> 02:04:51,450
Ďakujem.

2790
02:04:51,600 --> 02:04:52,850
Mirko!

2791
02:04:54,400 --> 02:04:55,890
By si mi potom mohol aj

2792
02:04:55,890 --> 02:04:57,200
pedikúru porobiť.

2793
02:04:57,200 --> 02:04:59,730
Otrasné mám tie nohy, jak tak kukám.

2794
02:05:02,890 --> 02:05:04,420
Ale, už vidím, že tuto

2795
02:05:04,420 --> 02:05:07,150
pán darca začína byť nervózny.

2796
02:05:07,880 --> 02:05:09,790
Asi už pomaličky tuší,

2797
02:05:11,010 --> 02:05:12,890
že mu bude odkrojené

2798
02:05:12,890 --> 02:05:14,090
zo ksichtíčku.

2799
02:05:14,670 --> 02:05:16,710
Od prvého momentu si bol pre mňa

2800
02:05:16,710 --> 02:05:18,010
čiernym koňom, Dano.

2801
02:05:18,010 --> 02:05:19,830
Alebo ako sa v Anglicku hovorí,

2802
02:05:19,830 --> 02:05:21,500
black horse, samozrejme.

2803
02:05:22,460 --> 02:05:23,700
Vybral som si síce

2804
02:05:23,700 --> 02:05:25,280
troch iných súťaziacich,

2805
02:05:25,720 --> 02:05:27,650
ale nedalo mi to a na poslednú chvíľu

2806
02:05:27,650 --> 02:05:29,370
som si musel zvoliť aj teba.

2807
02:05:30,010 --> 02:05:31,640
No a môj inštinkt sa nemýlil,

2808
02:05:31,640 --> 02:05:33,720
od prvej disciplíny dokazovala

2809
02:05:33,720 --> 02:05:35,380
tvoja koža, že je výnimočná.

2810
02:05:35,380 --> 02:05:38,470
Najskôr zvládla teplo dračieho ohňa bez ujmy,

2811
02:05:38,470 --> 02:05:40,110
potom krásne zareagovala

2812
02:05:40,110 --> 02:05:41,560
na harmančekový kúpeľ.

2813
02:05:41,560 --> 02:05:43,590
No a nakoniec sa vôbec nepoškodila

2814
02:05:43,590 --> 02:05:44,580
po hodine

2815
02:05:45,670 --> 02:05:46,840
v ľadovom rybníku.

2816
02:05:48,800 --> 02:05:50,370
Za celú tu dobu, Dano,

2817
02:05:51,160 --> 02:05:52,940
ti nevyrašil jediný jebák!

2818
02:05:53,670 --> 02:05:55,020
Vďaka tvojej tváričke

2819
02:05:55,020 --> 02:05:56,760
zažije slovenská scéna...

2820
02:05:58,000 --> 02:05:59,160
návrat...

2821
02:05:59,890 --> 02:06:00,890
Mekyho

2822
02:06:02,440 --> 02:06:03,700
Žbirku.

2823
02:06:20,190 --> 02:06:22,340
Už prestaň prdieť ten čpavok,

2824
02:06:22,340 --> 02:06:24,020
lebo mi odjebe nosohltan.

2825
02:06:24,720 --> 02:06:26,620
Poďme teda na operáciu.

2826
02:06:28,310 --> 02:06:29,890
Neváľaj sa Drevo, vstávaj.

2827
02:06:29,890 --> 02:06:30,590
Get up!

2828
02:06:30,730 --> 02:06:32,170
Slušnosť káže, že

2829
02:06:32,170 --> 02:06:34,170
v prítomnosti najväčšej megastar

2830
02:06:34,170 --> 02:06:35,500
slovenskej popmusic

2831
02:06:35,500 --> 02:06:37,080
sa treba pokloniť.

2832
02:06:37,350 --> 02:06:39,330
Keď má človek zastavené vetry,

2833
02:06:39,330 --> 02:06:41,120
tak sa odporúča predkláňať.

2834
02:06:41,160 --> 02:06:42,790
Uvidíš, jak sa ti uľaví.

2835
02:06:43,010 --> 02:06:43,650
Pome.

2836
02:06:44,000 --> 02:06:44,560
Pome!

2837
02:06:46,940 --> 02:06:47,920
Oh my god,

2838
02:06:47,920 --> 02:06:50,480
ty tu zasmradíš celý cintorín.

2839
02:06:50,890 --> 02:06:52,140
Ty epileptik!

2840
02:06:56,810 --> 02:06:58,140
No dobre, že si

2841
02:06:58,140 --> 02:07:00,400
neprivlastňujem aj tvoje črevá.

2842
02:07:00,810 --> 02:07:02,030
Alebo kokot.

2843
02:07:02,470 --> 02:07:03,510
Som počul,

2844
02:07:04,100 --> 02:07:06,080
že máš v trenkách mini verziu.

2845
02:07:05,850 --> 02:07:06,500
Nemám!

2846
02:07:08,620 --> 02:07:10,660
Zajtra na koncerte padne

2847
02:07:10,660 --> 02:07:11,850
Čierny Balog.

2848
02:07:12,240 --> 02:07:14,790
A budú ma hrávať všetky rádiá.

2849
02:07:17,660 --> 02:07:18,770
Ty ani nevieš,

2850
02:07:19,120 --> 02:07:21,420
ako mi vaši profesori pomohli.

2851
02:07:22,180 --> 02:07:23,730
Len vďaka nim som sa dostal

2852
02:07:23,730 --> 02:07:25,750
k slzám afgánskych polosirôt

2853
02:07:25,750 --> 02:07:28,370
a Arabskému rituálu znovuzrodenia.

2854
02:07:29,350 --> 02:07:31,460
Hlavne jeden profesor mi pomáhal

2855
02:07:31,460 --> 02:07:32,960
rovno pod vaším nosom

2856
02:07:32,960 --> 02:07:34,580
a nikto si to nevšimol.

2857
02:07:35,710 --> 02:07:36,590
Nobody.

2858
02:07:37,680 --> 02:07:38,740
Dosť bolo kecov,

2859
02:07:38,740 --> 02:07:40,580
prichádza vrchol večera.

2860
02:07:40,920 --> 02:07:42,100
Ti odrežem hlavu

2861
02:07:42,100 --> 02:07:43,530
ešte kým je teplá.

2862
02:07:44,250 --> 02:07:45,380
Jožko Vajda!

2863
02:07:46,320 --> 02:07:47,410
Pakuj sa sem, inak

2864
02:07:47,410 --> 02:07:48,510
začnem spievať.

2865
02:07:48,510 --> 02:07:49,780
Viem, že nemáš rád moju

2866
02:07:49,780 --> 02:07:51,140
dokonalú tvorbu!

2867
02:07:51,560 --> 02:07:52,550
Tie dni,

2868
02:07:52,730 --> 02:07:54,220
keď sa cítim

2869
02:07:54,220 --> 02:07:55,840
veľmi clivo,

2870
02:07:56,160 --> 02:07:57,570
vyfajčil

2871
02:07:57,570 --> 02:07:58,830
by som aj

2872
02:07:58,830 --> 02:08:00,480
McCartneyho.

2873
02:08:00,930 --> 02:08:02,340
Beatles kopírujem

2874
02:08:02,340 --> 02:08:03,680
odjakživa.

2875
02:08:04,090 --> 02:08:05,330
Moja sláva je

2876
02:08:05,330 --> 02:08:06,720
nespravodlivá.

2877
02:08:05,900 --> 02:08:06,700
Stačilo.

2878
02:08:08,960 --> 02:08:09,940
Jožo Vajda!

2879
02:08:08,960 --> 02:08:09,940
Jožko Vajda!

2880
02:08:13,360 --> 02:08:15,070
Paul McCartney. Paul McCartney.

2881
02:08:15,070 --> 02:08:16,970
Paul McCartneyho. Paul McCartney.

2882
02:08:16,970 --> 02:08:18,970
Paul McCartney býva za rohom.

2883
02:08:18,970 --> 02:08:20,700
V bufete stojí Ringo Starr.

2884
02:08:20,700 --> 02:08:22,220
Beatles. Pete Brown.

2885
02:08:22,220 --> 02:08:23,920
Eric Clapton. J. Bruce.

2886
02:08:23,920 --> 02:08:25,730
Georgea Martina. Phil Collins.

2887
02:08:25,730 --> 02:08:26,450
Yesterday.

2888
02:08:26,450 --> 02:08:27,850
Red Rose Speedway.

2889
02:08:27,850 --> 02:08:29,190
Good chords. Follow me.

2890
02:08:29,190 --> 02:08:30,320
I want to hold your hand.

2891
02:08:30,320 --> 02:08:32,150
Oh yeah, got a something.

2892
02:08:52,260 --> 02:08:53,260


2893
02:09:10,940 --> 02:09:12,420
Dano, sme tvoji mŕtvi fotrovci.

2894
02:09:12,420 --> 02:09:13,440
Vždy sme ťa nenávideli,

2895
02:09:13,440 --> 02:09:14,660
ale ešte viac sme neznášali

2896
02:09:14,660 --> 02:09:15,700
tvorbu Mekyho Žbirku.

2897
02:09:15,700 --> 02:09:17,700
Preto ti pomôžeme s útekom odtiaľto.

2898
02:09:22,410 --> 02:09:23,650
Dano, odnes ma naspäť,

2899
02:09:23,650 --> 02:09:25,490
nech mi otec môže vythnúť zlaté zuby

2900
02:09:25,490 --> 02:09:26,960
a predať ich do záložne.

2901
02:09:27,520 --> 02:09:28,390
Daniel,

2902
02:09:28,560 --> 02:09:29,980
nikdy sme ťa nechceli.

2903
02:09:30,790 --> 02:09:32,020
Bola som na potrate, ale

2904
02:09:32,020 --> 02:09:33,450
pán doktor ho dojebal.

2905
02:09:33,450 --> 02:09:35,450
Tak bež už, ty pankhart.

2906
02:09:35,450 --> 02:09:36,990
Bež!

2907
02:09:39,760 --> 02:09:40,700
Sem poď!

2908
02:09:44,840 --> 02:09:45,990
Kde je?!

2909
02:09:46,740 --> 02:09:48,960
No!

2910
02:09:49,690 --> 02:09:50,750
Tak dámy a páni,

2911
02:09:50,750 --> 02:09:52,070
máme tu víťazov!

2912
02:09:52,070 --> 02:09:53,500
Drevo tam nejak fňuká,

2913
02:09:53,500 --> 02:09:55,080
ktovie, čo mu Šaňo ujebal,

2914
02:09:55,080 --> 02:09:56,680
že tak strašne vreští.

2915
02:09:57,280 --> 02:09:58,250
Ale pozor,

2916
02:09:58,680 --> 02:10:00,740
vyzerá to tak, že Šaňo Fekete

2917
02:10:01,080 --> 02:10:02,440
zdechol jak taký

2918
02:10:02,440 --> 02:10:04,920
všivavý pes!

2919
02:10:06,600 --> 02:10:07,870
To sú mi veci dámy a páni!

2920
02:10:07,870 --> 02:10:08,910
To sú mi veci.

2921
02:10:09,310 --> 02:10:09,990
Danko.

2922
02:10:10,660 --> 02:10:11,880
Nedotýkaj sa ho,

2923
02:10:12,090 --> 02:10:13,690
dotkni sa radšej mňa.

2924
02:10:12,920 --> 02:10:13,420
Nie!

2925
02:10:13,760 --> 02:10:14,410
Danko.

2926
02:10:15,440 --> 02:10:15,940
Dano.

2927
02:10:16,290 --> 02:10:17,020
Láska.

2928
02:10:17,160 --> 02:10:18,270
Šesťnasť

2929
02:10:19,000 --> 02:10:19,750
eur.

2930
02:10:20,860 --> 02:10:21,880
Mi dlžil ten

2931
02:10:21,880 --> 02:10:23,150
Cigán pojebaný.

2932
02:10:23,150 --> 02:10:24,490
Šetril som si na

2933
02:10:24,490 --> 02:10:25,780
operáciu

2934
02:10:26,400 --> 02:10:27,650
očí.

2935
02:10:27,380 --> 02:10:28,010
Danko,

2936
02:10:28,570 --> 02:10:30,600
ty si tak krásny, keď plačeš.

2937
02:10:31,000 --> 02:10:33,000
Milujem ťa z celého srdca.

2938
02:10:33,210 --> 02:10:34,630
Skapal najväčší dlžník

2939
02:10:34,920 --> 02:10:35,990
na tejto škole.

2940
02:10:35,880 --> 02:10:36,560
A kurva.

2941
02:10:39,480 --> 02:10:41,640
No šak nič také hrozné

2942
02:10:41,640 --> 02:10:43,300
sa nestalo.

2943
02:10:44,740 --> 02:10:46,360
Pustite ma vy kurvy!

2944
02:10:49,350 --> 02:10:50,710
Dvestodvadsať eur!

2945
02:10:52,940 --> 02:10:54,850
Dvestodvadsať.

2946
02:10:57,250 --> 02:10:58,390
Som mu požičal

2947
02:10:58,390 --> 02:11:00,120
tento týždeň.

2948
02:11:04,120 --> 02:11:04,940
Nerev.

2949
02:11:04,940 --> 02:11:06,180
Ber to pozitívne.

2950
02:11:06,620 --> 02:11:08,270
Máme o jedného Cigáňa menej.

2951
02:11:14,220 --> 02:11:16,340
Boha, čo tí tam škriekajú.

2952
02:11:19,120 --> 02:11:21,120
Ja by som z toho spravil oslavu.

2953
02:11:20,580 --> 02:11:21,700
Hypotéka.

2954
02:11:21,700 --> 02:11:23,240
14 detí!

2955
02:11:23,330 --> 02:11:24,780
Ja som v piči.

2956
02:11:24,780 --> 02:11:26,080
Maroši, ty vogo!

2957
02:11:26,080 --> 02:11:27,860
To jako vážně tady masturbuješ?

2958
02:11:27,930 --> 02:11:29,800
Ty seš nekrofil pojebaný.

2959
02:11:30,120 --> 02:11:31,180
Chorá hlava.

2960
02:11:31,370 --> 02:11:32,370
[Martin Kelecsényi - Musím už ísť]

2961
02:11:45,280 --> 02:11:47,010
No nevrešti už toľko.

2962
02:12:00,470 --> 02:12:02,310
No nerev už toľko, Drevo!

2963
02:12:02,650 --> 02:12:03,450
Nerev.

2964
02:12:04,100 --> 02:12:04,710
Sadaj.

2965
02:12:06,100 --> 02:12:07,500
No neškriekaj už!

2966
02:12:09,070 --> 02:12:10,990
Vypijeme si Dano, čo hovoríš?

2967
02:12:10,990 --> 02:12:12,750
Mám tu dvanásťročnú slivku.

2968
02:12:12,910 --> 02:12:14,430
Nalejem poldeci, čo?

2969
02:12:14,840 --> 02:12:16,490
Mohli by sme sa najebať.

2970
02:12:16,650 --> 02:12:17,970
Vydezinfikujete mi

2971
02:12:17,970 --> 02:12:19,460
ranu, prosím?

2972
02:12:19,540 --> 02:12:20,880
Tento škrabanec?

2973
02:12:23,480 --> 02:12:25,350
Keď môjho deda mlátili Maďari,

2974
02:12:25,350 --> 02:12:27,010
trstenicou, to boli rany!

2975
02:12:27,620 --> 02:12:29,260
Som veľmi unavený

2976
02:12:29,320 --> 02:12:31,450
a točká sa mi hlavička.

2977
02:12:31,670 --> 02:12:32,530
Pojeb sa.

2978
02:12:32,630 --> 02:12:34,090
A povedz mi, prečo nemáš

2979
02:12:34,090 --> 02:12:35,450
oskalpovaný ksicht.

2980
02:12:36,020 --> 02:12:36,950
Prečo?

2981
02:12:38,300 --> 02:12:39,170
Au!

2982
02:12:41,170 --> 02:12:42,160
Pome radšej piť.

2983
02:12:42,950 --> 02:12:44,660
Začínam mať absťák.

2984
02:12:44,100 --> 02:12:44,930
Celý turnaj bol

2985
02:12:44,930 --> 02:12:46,580
jeden obrovský podvrh.

2986
02:12:47,100 --> 02:12:48,240
Žbirka sa zrýpal

2987
02:12:48,240 --> 02:12:49,250
do kyseliny

2988
02:12:49,250 --> 02:12:51,040
a hľadal darcu novej tváre.

2989
02:12:51,640 --> 02:12:53,640
Vyzerá ešte horšie, ako bežne.

2990
02:12:55,120 --> 02:12:56,640
Fantomas pojebaný.

2991
02:12:58,650 --> 02:13:00,440
Aj frňák mu to rozožralo.

2992
02:13:01,170 --> 02:13:02,530
Tie jeho riedke vlasy sú

2993
02:13:02,530 --> 02:13:03,750
nenávratne preč.

2994
02:13:06,010 --> 02:13:07,700
Meky spomínal, že mu celý čas

2995
02:13:07,700 --> 02:13:09,140
pomáhal jeden z učiteľov.

2996
02:13:09,140 --> 02:13:10,790
Neviete, kto by to mohol byť?

2997
02:13:10,900 --> 02:13:11,920
Musel to byť Kolman.

2998
02:13:11,920 --> 02:13:13,920
Však mu aj predal tie arabské slzy.

2999
02:13:13,920 --> 02:13:15,480
Bol to určite Kolman.

3000
02:13:15,510 --> 02:13:16,140
Kolman?

3001
02:13:17,360 --> 02:13:18,540
Kolman to teda nebol.

3002
02:13:18,540 --> 02:13:19,450
Tak kto teda?

3003
02:13:22,510 --> 02:13:24,270
Keď tak nad tým premýšľam,

3004
02:13:24,660 --> 02:13:26,840
tak vy ste mali vždy celkom rád

3005
02:13:26,980 --> 02:13:29,210
Mira Žbirku, pán profesor.

3006
02:13:36,370 --> 02:13:38,280
No, zavše si vypočujem

3007
02:13:38,280 --> 02:13:39,770
dáký jeho song.

3008
02:13:41,680 --> 02:13:42,940
Vaša generácia nevie

3009
02:13:42,940 --> 02:13:44,150
čo je dobrá muzika!

3010
02:13:44,340 --> 02:13:46,210
Meky vedel s jednou mŕtvou gitarou

3011
02:13:46,210 --> 02:13:47,290
spraviť takú show, že

3012
02:13:47,290 --> 02:13:49,380
v kultúrnych domoch zvlhli ešte aj steny!

3013
02:13:52,190 --> 02:13:53,860
Kurva, kde je ten chlast?!

3014
02:13:54,980 --> 02:13:56,630
S novou tvárou a novým imidžom

3015
02:13:56,630 --> 02:13:58,020
by mohol Žbirka koncertovať

3016
02:13:58,020 --> 02:14:00,100
ďalších dvadsať rokov, až do deväťdesiatky!

3017
02:14:00,290 --> 02:14:01,650
Potreboval niekoho, kto ho

3018
02:14:01,650 --> 02:14:02,720
opäť vráti na výslnie

3019
02:14:02,720 --> 02:14:03,820
a garantujem ti,

3020
02:14:04,130 --> 02:14:05,950
že Kolman to teda nebol.

3021
02:14:06,230 --> 02:14:07,510
Zosnovať takýto plán

3022
02:14:07,510 --> 02:14:09,180
vyžadovalo silnú myseľ!

3023
02:14:09,350 --> 02:14:11,060
Tak trochu porozmýšľaj, ty somár.

3024
02:14:17,540 --> 02:14:19,180
Starý Jano sa správal

3025
02:14:19,180 --> 02:14:21,240
nejak divne v poslednej dobe.

3026
02:14:21,820 --> 02:14:22,900
Žeby on bol tou

3027
02:14:22,900 --> 02:14:24,370
megamysľou za týmto?

3028
02:14:24,300 --> 02:14:25,840
Starý Jano! Ach Drevo.

3029
02:14:25,980 --> 02:14:27,980
Otvor si oči, ty teľa sprosté.

3030
02:14:28,330 --> 02:14:29,900
To ja som všetko zosnoval!

3031
02:14:29,900 --> 02:14:31,120
Ja som ušiel z väzenia!

3032
02:14:31,120 --> 02:14:32,490
Ja som Mekyho postrčil

3033
02:14:32,490 --> 02:14:33,870
v Patinciach do kyseliny.

3034
02:14:34,890 --> 02:14:36,960
Ja som u Kolmana zistil informácie

3035
02:14:36,960 --> 02:14:38,470
o rituále znovuzrodenia.

3036
02:14:41,170 --> 02:14:42,860
Len vďaka mne sa Meky vráti

3037
02:14:42,860 --> 02:14:43,950
opäť na scénu.

3038
02:14:47,060 --> 02:14:49,080
Ten starý buzerant už začína

3039
02:14:49,080 --> 02:14:50,110
niečo tušiť.

3040
02:14:50,870 --> 02:14:52,010
Takže ti ten ksicht

3041
02:14:52,010 --> 02:14:53,670
odrežem hneď teraz.

3042
02:14:53,890 --> 02:14:54,680
No a Meky

3043
02:14:56,140 --> 02:14:57,570
bude mať ešte dnes večer

3044
02:14:57,570 --> 02:14:58,720
novú identitu.

3045
02:14:59,310 --> 02:15:00,120
Jožko-

3046
02:15:00,470 --> 02:15:01,630
Už idem, Danko!

3047
02:15:05,480 --> 02:15:06,410
Ľudo, nalej mu tie

3048
02:15:06,410 --> 02:15:07,530
slzy do gágora.

3049
02:15:13,050 --> 02:15:14,660
Kde je pravý Jozef Šlota?

3050
02:15:15,520 --> 02:15:16,870
Vylíž mi riť, starec.

3051
02:15:17,030 --> 02:15:18,900
Nečítaj mi myšlienky a odpovedaj!

3052
02:15:18,900 --> 02:15:20,740
Napľujem na hrob tvojej materi.

3053
02:15:20,440 --> 02:15:21,730
Ja už som starý človek,

3054
02:15:21,730 --> 02:15:23,280
nemôžem sa toľko čertiť!

3055
02:15:23,280 --> 02:15:24,310
Kde je Šlota?!

3056
02:15:26,340 --> 02:15:27,060
Uhni, kokot.

3057
02:15:38,230 --> 02:15:42,760
...bratia, veď sa ony stratia.

3058
02:15:42,760 --> 02:15:46,570
Slováci ožijú

3059
02:15:46,900 --> 02:15:47,730
To Slo-

3060
02:15:48,690 --> 02:15:49,730
Dobrý večer.

3061
02:15:49,890 --> 02:15:52,030
Je SNS stále v parlamente?

3062
02:15:52,130 --> 02:15:53,800
SNS? Čo mu jebe?

3063
02:15:56,590 --> 02:15:57,870
To je popper, vážení.

3064
02:15:58,350 --> 02:15:59,150
Tak mi tam trošku

3065
02:15:59,150 --> 02:16:00,290
nechaj na večer, Ľudo.

3066
02:16:01,580 --> 02:16:02,370
Neboj Jožko,

3067
02:16:02,370 --> 02:16:03,790
SNS je stále tam.

3068
02:16:04,910 --> 02:16:05,910
[Miro Žbirka - Pekný chlapec]

3069
02:16:35,440 --> 02:16:36,270
Kto to je?

3070
02:16:37,240 --> 02:16:38,920
Daj sem ten tvoj ksichtík!

3071
02:16:38,110 --> 02:16:40,600
Ruky preč od Danka, oplan jeden špinavý.

3072
02:16:42,420 --> 02:16:44,420
Jerguš Gombit, ja som to tušil.

3073
02:16:45,260 --> 02:16:47,180
Meky vydá album aj bez tvojej tváre.

3074
02:16:47,180 --> 02:16:48,070
Pozri.

3075
02:16:50,420 --> 02:16:51,410
Ty sa pozri.

3076
02:16:51,760 --> 02:16:53,930
Čo mu tvoj prestarnutý idol spravil!

3077
02:16:55,840 --> 02:16:57,150
Bude to album roka, je tam aj

3078
02:16:57,150 --> 02:16:58,540
remix bieleho kvetu.

3079
02:16:59,440 --> 02:17:00,150
Aj duet

3080
02:17:02,000 --> 02:17:03,770
s dvojníkom Paula McCartneyho.

3081
02:17:04,750 --> 02:17:05,790
Chcel som tomu

3082
02:17:05,790 --> 02:17:06,810
zabrániť.

3083
02:17:07,650 --> 02:17:09,770
Ihneď zoberte toho blázna do väzby.

3084
02:17:10,190 --> 02:17:11,630
Je psychicky narušený.

3085
02:17:11,890 --> 02:17:13,070
Prišiel čas Žbirku,

3086
02:17:13,070 --> 02:17:14,490
bude sedieť na tróne!

3087
02:17:15,470 --> 02:17:17,110
A ty na elektrickom kresle.

3088
02:17:17,400 --> 02:17:18,430
Poď Danko, vyzleč sa,

3089
02:17:18,430 --> 02:17:19,740
prezriem ti tie škrabance.

3090
02:17:19,740 --> 02:17:22,310
Neudrel ťa náhodou Meky aj v oblasti...

3091
02:17:22,000 --> 02:17:23,300
Ó, veľký Alah,

3092
02:17:23,300 --> 02:17:25,900
odpusť tejto zblúdilej duši.

3093
02:17:26,040 --> 02:17:27,040


3094
02:17:38,150 --> 02:17:40,150
Šaňo Fekete

3095
02:17:41,690 --> 02:17:43,690
bol jednoduchý chlapec.

3096
02:17:46,250 --> 02:17:48,590
Miloval tanec, sociálne dávky

3097
02:17:49,680 --> 02:17:51,640
a svoju vlastnú sestru.

3098
02:17:52,530 --> 02:17:54,290
Ale zo všetkého najviac

3099
02:17:54,520 --> 02:17:56,520
miloval požičané peniaze.

3100
02:17:57,180 --> 02:17:58,600
Bolesť jeho straty

3101
02:17:59,220 --> 02:18:00,440
ostane navždy

3102
02:18:00,970 --> 02:18:02,470
v každom z nás.

3103
02:18:03,700 --> 02:18:05,210
Pretože každému z nás

3104
02:18:05,210 --> 02:18:07,210
dlžil tento Romák nejaké peniaze.

3105
02:18:08,200 --> 02:18:09,200
Každému.

3106
02:18:10,920 --> 02:18:11,710
Nazdravie.

3107
02:18:11,480 --> 02:18:12,440
Šaňo Fekete

3108
02:18:13,700 --> 02:18:15,150
bol skurvený žebrák,

3109
02:18:15,150 --> 02:18:16,820
ktorý bez hanby utrácal

3110
02:18:16,820 --> 02:18:18,690
naše ťažko ušetrené peniaze

3111
02:18:18,690 --> 02:18:20,650
za toluén a automaty.

3112
02:18:21,310 --> 02:18:23,200
Všetci dôverne poznáme jeho

3113
02:18:23,200 --> 02:18:25,460
prosby o eurko, dve na chleba.

3114
02:18:25,460 --> 02:18:27,870
Nejaké drobné na cestu do Ružomberka.

3115
02:18:28,040 --> 02:18:30,040
Alebo almužníčku pre chorú mamu.

3116
02:18:30,470 --> 02:18:32,290
A všetci sme v dobrej viere

3117
02:18:32,290 --> 02:18:34,290
na tieto klamstvá skočili.

3118
02:18:34,380 --> 02:18:36,770
Či už žiaci, alebo učitelia.

3119
02:18:37,160 --> 02:18:39,420
Mama, neotravuj ma, som na pohrebe.

3120
02:18:40,240 --> 02:18:41,390
Ale takého kokota.

3121
02:18:42,300 --> 02:18:43,240
Dobre, dobre...

3122
02:18:41,390 --> 02:18:43,350
Z týchto dôvodov sme sa rozhodli

3123
02:18:43,350 --> 02:18:45,270
Šaňa Feketeho spopolniť

3124
02:18:45,270 --> 02:18:47,200
a pridať jeho telesné zostatky

3125
02:18:47,200 --> 02:18:48,930
do detských zásypov.

3126
02:18:49,120 --> 02:18:50,940
Celý život nás mal u riti.

3127
02:18:51,100 --> 02:18:53,100
Tak teraz ho budeme mať u riti my.

3128
02:18:54,140 --> 02:18:55,390
So Šaňom Feketem

3129
02:18:55,390 --> 02:18:56,960
odišlo neuveriteľných

3130
02:18:56,960 --> 02:18:59,940
17344€

3131
02:18:59,940 --> 02:19:01,920
a mnohé vypožičané predmety.

3132
02:19:02,520 --> 02:19:03,940
Odpočívajte v pokoji,

3133
02:19:03,940 --> 02:19:05,330
drahé peniaze,

3134
02:19:05,330 --> 02:19:06,380
forinty,

3135
02:19:06,380 --> 02:19:07,490
šperky,

3136
02:19:07,490 --> 02:19:08,720
autorádiá,

3137
02:19:08,720 --> 02:19:09,880
puklice,

3138
02:19:09,880 --> 02:19:11,530
starožitnosti,

3139
02:19:11,530 --> 02:19:12,740
hodinky,

3140
02:19:12,740 --> 02:19:13,870
karosérie,

3141
02:19:13,870 --> 02:19:14,980
elektronika,

3142
02:19:14,980 --> 02:19:16,160
pneumatiky,

3143
02:19:16,160 --> 02:19:17,250
bicykle,

3144
02:19:17,250 --> 02:19:18,640
chladiče,

3145
02:19:18,640 --> 02:19:20,140
dopravné značky,

3146
02:19:20,140 --> 02:19:21,250
karburátory,

3147
02:19:21,250 --> 02:19:22,440
reťaze...

3148
02:19:26,150 --> 02:19:26,780
Nehoň si,

3149
02:19:26,780 --> 02:19:28,840
budeš to semeno o chvíľu potrebovať.

3150
02:19:29,580 --> 02:19:30,540
Viem, že máš teraz

3151
02:19:30,540 --> 02:19:32,020
problém s peniazmi, Dano.

3152
02:19:32,310 --> 02:19:34,080
To má po smrti Šaňa asi každý.

3153
02:19:36,610 --> 02:19:37,270
Ahoj.

3154
02:19:38,790 --> 02:19:40,190
Tak čo s tým spravíme?

3155
02:19:41,390 --> 02:19:43,390
Som ochotný ti pomôcť, Dano.

3156
02:19:44,250 --> 02:19:45,450
Myslím finančne.

3157
02:19:51,710 --> 02:19:53,600
Mám dvadsaťeurovku zrolovanú

3158
02:19:53,600 --> 02:19:54,710
v konečníku, Dano.

3159
02:19:55,000 --> 02:19:56,070
Chceš ju vytiahnuť?

3160
02:19:59,590 --> 02:20:00,290
Pane.

3161
02:20:01,700 --> 02:20:02,710
Ja už takto ďalej

3162
02:20:02,710 --> 02:20:04,100
nemôžem pokračovať.

3163
02:20:05,320 --> 02:20:06,500
Vaše semeno

3164
02:20:06,930 --> 02:20:08,100
viem degustovať

3165
02:20:08,100 --> 02:20:09,650
na viacerých úrovniach.

3166
02:20:10,270 --> 02:20:11,500
Chcem sa pohnúť ďalej.

3167
02:20:11,210 --> 02:20:12,970
Bzdocha bezcitná.

3168
02:20:18,030 --> 02:20:19,770
Požiadal si o prestup

3169
02:20:21,100 --> 02:20:22,240
na inú školu?

3170
02:20:23,630 --> 02:20:24,630
Teraz ma počúvaj,

3171
02:20:24,630 --> 02:20:25,310
ty hyena.

3172
02:20:25,310 --> 02:20:26,830
Dokiaľ ja budem riaditeľom

3173
02:20:26,830 --> 02:20:27,930
tejto školy, tak ti

3174
02:20:27,930 --> 02:20:29,080
všetky prestupy

3175
02:20:29,080 --> 02:20:30,000
zmietnem zo stolu.

3176
02:20:30,000 --> 02:20:31,610
To ti tu odprisahávam,

3177
02:20:31,610 --> 02:20:32,360
ty hajzel.

3178
02:20:34,160 --> 02:20:35,150
Fajčiť mi kokot

3179
02:20:35,150 --> 02:20:36,820
je tvoj životný údel.

3180
02:20:37,120 --> 02:20:38,080
Si vyvolený.

3181
02:20:39,460 --> 02:20:40,580
Vždy si bol.

3182
02:20:41,740 --> 02:20:43,360
Tak sa trochu vschop, Dano

3183
02:20:43,360 --> 02:20:44,500
a vyhoď si takéto

3184
02:20:44,500 --> 02:20:45,830
pičoviny z hlavy.

3185
02:20:47,720 --> 02:20:48,700
Ostávaš tu.

3186
02:20:50,800 --> 02:20:51,670
O päť minút budem

3187
02:20:51,670 --> 02:20:53,310
v kabinete len v podväzkoch.

3188
02:20:54,030 --> 02:20:55,150
Dvere nezamykám.

3189
02:20:55,810 --> 02:20:56,950
Zasran jeden,

3190
02:20:56,950 --> 02:20:58,670
že prestup na inú školu.

3191
02:20:59,170 --> 02:21:00,860
A tak sa končil jeden

3192
02:21:00,860 --> 02:21:02,950
zvláštny rok na Rokforte.

3193
02:21:03,320 --> 02:21:05,170
Gábor si pri lúčení vyhliadol

3194
02:21:05,170 --> 02:21:06,810
Kim, a kedže vždy túžil

3195
02:21:06,810 --> 02:21:08,760
po jebačke s transsexuálom,

3196
02:21:08,760 --> 02:21:09,950
rozhodol sa...

3197
02:21:10,200 --> 02:21:10,640
Kim.

3198
02:21:11,010 --> 02:21:12,500
Dvadsaťtisíc forintov

3199
02:21:12,500 --> 02:21:13,600
na operáció.

3200
02:21:14,030 --> 02:21:15,890
Keby Štefan, zavolaj mne.

3201
02:21:15,930 --> 02:21:17,100
Budem čakať.

3202
02:21:18,000 --> 02:21:18,770
Szia.

3203
02:21:21,040 --> 02:21:22,630
Peder, ten v ten deň

3204
02:21:22,630 --> 02:21:24,280
dostal posledné bozky

3205
02:21:24,280 --> 02:21:25,600
svojho života.

3206
02:21:25,860 --> 02:21:26,930
Au revoir.

3207
02:21:28,560 --> 02:21:30,670
(Jebem ťa, ty skurvysyn.)

3208
02:21:34,190 --> 02:21:35,070
A Dano,

3209
02:21:35,230 --> 02:21:37,310
ten ako obvykle len bezducho

3210
02:21:37,310 --> 02:21:39,070
chodil, sledujúc tú zmes

3211
02:21:39,070 --> 02:21:40,810
rôznych rás a podrás.

3212
02:21:41,040 --> 02:21:42,520
Ako si falošne sľubujú,

3213
02:21:42,520 --> 02:21:43,590
že si napíšu.

3214
02:21:44,110 --> 02:21:45,480
A popritom rozmýšľal,

3215
02:21:45,480 --> 02:21:46,910
kde by sa tak mohol

3216
02:21:46,910 --> 02:21:48,170
čo najskôr vysrať,

3217
02:21:48,380 --> 02:21:50,380
pretože to naňho znova prichádzalo.

3218
02:21:55,660 --> 02:21:57,740
Francúzske kurvy boli vyprevádzané

3219
02:21:57,740 --> 02:21:59,290
mohutným potleskom.

3220
02:21:59,570 --> 02:22:01,330
Dvanásť z nich ani netušilo,

3221
02:22:01,330 --> 02:22:03,180
že sa im v maternici vyvíja

3222
02:22:03,180 --> 02:22:04,450
malé bábätko.

3223
02:22:05,060 --> 02:22:06,570
To Gábor zas netušil,

3224
02:22:06,570 --> 02:22:08,570
že je otcom piatich z nich.

3225
02:22:11,430 --> 02:22:13,160
Žbirka ruší krst albumu

3226
02:22:13,160 --> 02:22:14,460
aj všetky koncerty.

3227
02:22:14,460 --> 02:22:15,260
Čo?

3228
02:22:15,860 --> 02:22:17,000
Neuveriteľné.

3229
02:22:17,620 --> 02:22:18,650
Ako som mohol toho

3230
02:22:18,650 --> 02:22:19,850
podliaka počúvať?

3231
02:22:24,350 --> 02:22:25,460
Už nikdy nebudem to

3232
02:22:25,460 --> 02:22:26,840
krehké dievča, čo?

3233
02:22:34,850 --> 02:22:35,450
Nikdy.

3234
02:22:40,940 --> 02:22:42,490
Ale budete ma podporovať.

3235
02:22:43,010 --> 02:22:43,880
Že, chlapci?

3236
02:22:44,660 --> 02:22:46,790
Dobre ti tie hormóny dojebali hlas.

3237
02:22:47,690 --> 02:22:48,260
Dano,

3238
02:22:48,470 --> 02:22:49,360
aspoň ty.

3239
02:22:49,570 --> 02:22:50,860
Jasné, Števko.

3240
02:22:56,440 --> 02:22:57,210
Počujte.

3241
02:22:57,680 --> 02:22:59,120
Kto je to ten Maroš?

3242
02:23:00,580 --> 02:23:02,860
To ostane asi navždy záhadou.

3243
02:23:04,090 --> 02:23:05,750
To bol teda rok.

3244
02:23:05,960 --> 02:23:08,380
Ďalšie roky na Rokforte boli kludnejšie

3245
02:23:08,380 --> 02:23:09,940
a nič výrazné sa neudialo.

3246
02:23:10,300 --> 02:23:11,590
Teda až na pandémiu

3247
02:23:11,590 --> 02:23:12,940
mykózy nôh, na ktorú

3248
02:23:12,940 --> 02:23:14,550
umreli tri štvrtiny študentov.

3249
02:23:15,350 --> 02:23:16,440
Meky Žbirka sa vzdal

3250
02:23:16,440 --> 02:23:18,280
svojej speváckej kariéry a začal

3251
02:23:18,280 --> 02:23:19,580
točiť cukrovú vatu na

3252
02:23:19,580 --> 02:23:21,140
kolotočoch v Šamoríne.

3253
02:23:21,370 --> 02:23:22,340
A Dano Drevo,

3254
02:23:22,760 --> 02:23:24,090
to je živý dôkaz toho,

3255
02:23:24,090 --> 02:23:25,560
že aj obyčajný človek,

3256
02:23:25,560 --> 02:23:27,170
ktorý sa vie jedine posrať,

3257
02:23:27,570 --> 02:23:29,740
sa môže stať legendou.

3258
02:23:31,940 --> 02:23:33,870
Maroš, jebni tam už titulky!

3259
02:23:35,520 --> 02:23:36,520
[Fall Out Boy - I Don't Care]

3260
02:23:37,320 --> 02:23:39,320
Titulky Dano Drevo a Turnaj Mekyho Žbirku

3261
02:23:39,320 --> 02:23:41,320
v0.6.2

3262
02:23:41,320 --> 02:23:43,320
by Mravec

